17%.<ref name=\":0\" /> The ports difficulties of flow in the port areas can be categorized into four different areas: the difficulties of flow in the port areas, the constraints to the rail model, the poor utilization of the capacity of the maritime terminals and the congestion in accesses. <ref name=\":0\" />\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== See also ==\n*[[Santos Brasil]]\n\n== External links==\n{{commonscat|Port of Santos}}\n* [http://www.portodesantos.com.br/ Official website] (in [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]])\n\n[[Category:Ports and harbours of Brazil]]\n[[Category:Santos, S\u00e3o Paulo]]\n", "name_user": "177.141.230.132", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Port_of_Santos"}
